com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row

Class DegenerateContextDataRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.basic.WrappedDataRow
      • com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row.DegenerateContextDataRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataRow, ContextDataRow<DataRow>

    public class DegenerateContextDataRow
extends WrappedDataRow
implements ContextDataRow<DataRow>
    The DegenerateContextDataRow class provides a simple context data row which holds itself as a context. This class can be useful for situations where a ContextDataRow is required, but where the context will never be used.
